title: quiche recipe
description: tasty type of pie
---
§recipe
	§ingredients
		§l [/recipes/pate_brisee.html] 1 pâte brisée §/l
		400ml cream
        4 eggs
        200g grated cheese
        200g lardons (or ham or vegetables or anything really)
        salt and pepper
	§/ingredients

	§instructions
		preheat the oven around 180°c
		mix all the eggs in a bowl
		add the cream and mix pretty evenly
		then you can add all the meat/vegetables and half the cheese
		put the dough in a tart mold or anything appropriate
		pour the mixture in the dough
		bake for around 40 minutes
	§/instructionsp
§/recipe
